										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<h1 class="pgc-h-arrow-right" data-track="18">1.柑橘类水果的起源</h1>
<p data-track="4">柑橘家族的所有成员，基本都来自三位野生“祖宗”：<strong>枸橼、野生柚</strong>和<strong>野生宽皮橘</strong>。它们相互杂交得到了现有的柑橘大家庭。</p>
<p data-track="5"><strong>柚子 X 橘子 = 橙子</strong></p>
<p data-track="6"><strong>柚子 X 橙子 = 葡萄柚</strong></p>
<p data-track="7"><strong>橘子 X 橙子 = 柑</strong></p>
<p data-track="8"><strong>橙子 X 枸橼 = 柠檬</strong></p>
<p data-track="9"><strong>橘子 X 枸橼 = 青柠</strong></p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-160" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/ba2d75ea72c1b066577d8274d8b95721.png" width="680" height="953" alt="有关水果的几个冷知识，你知道几个？" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/ba2d75ea72c1b066577d8274d8b95721.png 680w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/ba2d75ea72c1b066577d8274d8b95721-214x300.png 214w" sizes="(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="10">柑橘类的水果虽然好吃，但是胡萝卜素含量比较高，一次吃太多会来不及代谢，让皮肤变黄，但是过一段时间就会恢复原样。</p>
<h1 class="pgc-h-arrow-right">2.水果放冰箱坏的更快？</h1>
<p data-track="12">香蕉、芒果、火龙果放冰箱，会坏得更快。因为他们都是热带水果，在冰箱冷藏室中低温会被冻伤。</p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-161" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/fc21f0c5469e2c8a2f468c2ed995c4f6-763x1024.jpg" width="763" height="1024" alt="有关水果的几个冷知识，你知道几个？" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/fc21f0c5469e2c8a2f468c2ed995c4f6-763x1024.jpg 763w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/fc21f0c5469e2c8a2f468c2ed995c4f6-224x300.jpg 224w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/fc21f0c5469e2c8a2f468c2ed995c4f6-768x1030.jpg 768w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/fc21f0c5469e2c8a2f468c2ed995c4f6.jpg 954w" sizes="(max-width: 763px) 100vw, 763px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<h1 class="pgc-h-arrow-right">3.柠檬维生素C含量高？</h1>
<p data-track="14">柠檬的维C含量只有22mg/100g，在果蔬领域不算高。真正需要补充维C，还不如吃冬枣（243mg/100g)，或者直接购买维C含片。</p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-162" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/6269575e979aa97adb2baf49fc652b26-1024x683.jpg" width="1024" height="683" alt="有关水果的几个冷知识，你知道几个？" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/6269575e979aa97adb2baf49fc652b26-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/6269575e979aa97adb2baf49fc652b26-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/6269575e979aa97adb2baf49fc652b26-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/6269575e979aa97adb2baf49fc652b26.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<h1 class="pgc-h-arrow-right">4.黄瓜没有美容效果</h1>
<p data-track="22">黄瓜的主要成分90%以上都是水。当用黄瓜片敷脸时，黄瓜的水分在皮肤上很快就会蒸发，起不到美容保湿效果。</p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-163" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/fa747d915bb15876bd6799b9fda4f5d3.jpg" width="1023" height="682" alt="有关水果的几个冷知识，你知道几个？" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/fa747d915bb15876bd6799b9fda4f5d3.jpg 1023w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/fa747d915bb15876bd6799b9fda4f5d3-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/fa747d915bb15876bd6799b9fda4f5d3-768x512.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1023px) 100vw, 1023px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<h1 class="pgc-h-arrow-right">5.香蕉不会对治疗便秘有帮助</h1>
<p data-track="24">治疗便秘饮食方面主要依靠膳食纤维。但是香蕉的膳食纤维含量并不高，相反，未熟透的香蕉含有鞣酸，吃了更容易引起便秘。</p>
<h1 class="pgc-h-arrow-right">6.葡萄皮上面的白霜不是农药残留</h1>
<p data-track="25">白霜是葡萄分泌的一种天然物质，叫齐墩果酸，有白霜说明葡萄新鲜。它对人体无害，用水也洗不掉，可以放心吃。</p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-164" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/537871a450fd3e0cf7070e8cb01590e3-1024x683.jpg" width="1024" height="683" alt="有关水果的几个冷知识，你知道几个？" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/537871a450fd3e0cf7070e8cb01590e3-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/537871a450fd3e0cf7070e8cb01590e3-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/537871a450fd3e0cf7070e8cb01590e3-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/537871a450fd3e0cf7070e8cb01590e3.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<h1 class="pgc-h-arrow-right">7.苹果皮的营养价值比果肉高？</h1>
<p data-track="26">真的，但还是不建议吃皮。苹果的农药残留较多，削皮吃更健康。并且一个苹果，按照重量计算，果皮的营养价值仅占整个苹果的1/9，世卫生组织也是建议吃苹果削皮。</p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-165" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/439c40f2a01a42f14185956efc749ee1.jpg" width="1023" height="682" alt="有关水果的几个冷知识，你知道几个？" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/439c40f2a01a42f14185956efc749ee1.jpg 1023w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/439c40f2a01a42f14185956efc749ee1-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/439c40f2a01a42f14185956efc749ee1-768x512.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1023px) 100vw, 1023px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="32">上面的七个冷知识，有多少是你不知道的了？</p>
]]></content:encoded>
					
		
		
